      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you\u2014she is a total showstopper! This car is in truly flawless condition; honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied this beauty from day one, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the dealership headache, this is the one for you. Come see it for yourself and fall in love!",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
